io.storj

Class Scope

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.storj.Scope

  • public class Scope
extends Object
    Represents all credentials you need to access data on the Storj network:
    • Satellite address in the form of "host:port"
    • ApiKey to access the satellite
    • EncryptionAccess for accessing the encrypted content
